---
import { timeline } from "../../lib/about-data";
---

<section class="history-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="history-layout">
      <div class="history-content">
        <h2>A History of Cooperation</h2>
        
        <div class="history-subsections">
          <div class="subsection">
            <h3>History of Salinas</h3>
            <p>From a small isolated parish to a thriving example of cooperative economics. In the 1970s, Salinas was one of the poorest communities in Ecuador.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="subsection">
            <h3>Development of Solidarity Economy</h3>
            <p>Starting with a small cheese factory, the community learned basic cooperative techniques and built a cooperative model where profits stayed local.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="subsection">
            <h3>Role of Father Antonio Polo</h3>
            <p>The story of Father Antonio Polo and the community's resilience. His vision of community empowerment through cooperative enterprise created a sustainable economic model.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="subsection">
            <h3>Growth from Cheese to 40+ Enterprises</h3>
            <p>Today, Salinas is home to 40+ community enterprises exporting products worldwide, from chocolate to textiles to mushrooms.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="subsection">
            <h3>UNESCO Recognition</h3>
            <p>Recognized internationally as a model of sustainable community development and solidarity economy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="timeline-box">
        <div class="timeline-content">
          {timeline.map((item) => (
            <div class="timeline-entry">
              <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
              <div class="timeline-text">
                <div class="timeline-year">{item.decade}</div>
                <div class="timeline-event">{item.title}</div>
                <div class="timeline-description">{item.description}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .history-section {
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    background: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .history-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
  }

  .history-subsections {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .subsection {
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .subsection h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .subsection p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .timeline-box {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    position: sticky;
    top: 150px;
  }

  .timeline-title {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .timeline-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-entry {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-entry:not(:last-child) {
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
  }

  .timeline-dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--primary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .timeline-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .timeline-year {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .timeline-event {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #333;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-description {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .history-layout {
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .timeline-box {
      top: 100px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .history-section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .history-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .timeline-box {
      position: static;
    }

    .subsection p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .history-section {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .timeline-box {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .timeline-title {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline-content {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline-entry:not(:last-child) {
      padding-bottom: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
